Package com.telenav.kivakit.filesystem.spi

Interface FileService

All Superinterfaces:
Broadcaster, ByteSized, CreatedAt, Deletable, FileSystemObjectService, Listener, Modifiable, ModifiedAt, NamedObject, Readable, ReadableResource, Receiver, Repeater, Resource, Resourceful, ResourcePathed, StringSource, Transceiver, Transmitter, UriIdentified, Writable, WritableResource
public interface FileService extends FileSystemObjectService, WritableResource
A service provider interface (SPI) for filesystem files. Adds renameTo(FileService) to the methods required by FileSystemObjectService.
